{"tid":1851281,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［緊急］香港人！攞返你哋Deadline Fighter嘅精神出嚟！","createTime":"2020-01-30T03:25:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-01T07:10:38.000Z","uid":313730,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"ec029670c966fa22553bed1d1a018dd7d26d63e0","tid":1851281,"uid":313730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:25:53.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;推上熱門&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大家唔好因爲個肺炎就淡左場運動先得㗎，聯署要人啊！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n記唔記得之前有手足整過份中文版嘅聯署<br />\n好鬼正㗎！不過竟然冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://act4hk.com/petition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fact4hk.com%2Fpetition&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=b88c249a\" target=\"_blank\">https://act4hk.com/petition</a><br />\n<br />\n依家有幾份聯署急需大家簽咗佢，雖然得返好少時間，但我相信各位Deadline Fighter一定做得到！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n第一份 <span style=\"color: red;\">［最緊急］</span>：呼籲重新檢討《香港人權及民主法》<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUWpo8V.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUWpo8V.jpg&h=bc255d38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=6b6fa20c\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-human-rights-and-democracy-act-time-do-evaluation</a><br />\n<br />\n第二份<span style=\"color: red;\">［緊急］</span>：立即推動香港普選計劃<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WHaYtBB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWHaYtBB.jpg&h=248c9f76&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=e2104d5a\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-universal-suffrage-plan</a><br />\n<br />\n第三份：反對香港政府實施嚴厲的國歌法侵犯一國兩制和言論自由<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKD7mXj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKD7mXj.jpg&h=31a1ab41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fhong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech&d=Ey%2FAc8I3uyYuTLy5d8l3rEx5KyfgaA76LUEybGJClr4%3D&h=1c37ebea\" target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/hong-kong-governments-hard-pressed-national-anthem-law-violates-one-country-two-systems-and-freedom-speech</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">提一提大家</span></span><br />\n寫完名同埋電郵地址之後<br />\n唔好簽完就算啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記得去返你嘅電郵地址<span style=\"color: red;\">確認</span>返👇🏻<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/46qBfi4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F46qBfi4.png&h=21b03661&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n見到呢句先係真正搞掂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AoLJEL4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAoLJEL4.png&h=9d2a7f40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知道大家最近都好擔心肺炎， 但我哋一定要比白宮班人知道<br />\n我哋係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">絕對絕對絕對</span>唔會忘記場運動，我哋仲未放棄，我哋仲打緊仗<br />\n所以唔該大家<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">幫手推下</span></span>，等更多人可以簽咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"79e12fec9788b0c118b76dfd19ca2749eae39473","tid":1851281,"uid":171855,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:28:26.000Z","msg":"推啊！Home Office簽一流啊！！！！"},{"pid":"919e47acc42f71031621d83e9fd39a877d5153a5","tid":1851281,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:29:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2a71445bf99bf3dd7efb2e29f1d8f7b7e482aea2","tid":1851281,"uid":166506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:30:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"96a90d040cd8161ad73a15975e1f2b395a1904f1","tid":1851281,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:31:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ecf5dffa421e6ef8c69eae2e725372f21dd134c2","tid":1851281,"uid":8776,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-30T03:36:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a0cea0b8866b